# CHRONOS Benchmark Intelligence — 爬虫目标配置 (v4.4)
# 用法: python scripts/crawler/benchmark_crawler.py --targets targets.csv
# 字段说明:
#   entity      — 实体标识（英文，用于目录命名）
#   name        — 标准名称（中英文均可）
#   ticker      — 股票代码（akshare 格式: 上交所如 600519, 深交所如 000001, 港股如 00700, 美股如 AAPL）
#   market      — A(沪深) / H(港股) / US(美股) / ADR
#   years       — 爬取财年，逗号分隔
#   source_pref — 数据源偏好: akshare / eastmoney / manual
#   gics_group  — GICS行业组
entity,name,ticker,market,years,source_pref,gics_group
apple,Apple Inc.,AAPL,US,"2022,2023,2024",akshare,Information Technology
microsoft,Microsoft Corp.,MSFT,US,"2022,2023,2024",akshare,Information Technology
maotai,贵州茅台,600519,A,"2022,2023,2024",akshare,Consumer Staples
tencent,腾讯控股,00700,H,"2022,2023,2024",akshare,Communication Services
